"722","Additional Information About Minimum Required Investment"
"723","Shareholders can open a fund account with as little as $500 and"
"724","make subsequent investments in any amount. The minimum"
"725","investment is waived if you make regular investments weekly,"
"726","semi-monthly, or monthly through automatic deductions through"
"727","your bank checking or savings account. Currently, Putnam is"
"728","waiving the minimum, but reserves the right to reject initial"
"729","investments under the minimum."
